Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎並不只有你一個人看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見...什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 回答我 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻一個人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我說啊 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 之前你不是來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再...再一次 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有介意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你和你的朋友說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我的人生沒有任何影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說什麼啊 真是不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要被說成可愛 又不是老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝...謝謝 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你摔下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也 像面麻那樣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 面麻 在你那裡出現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然對面麻... 是喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的是因為喜歡才能看到實際上看不到的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是說「我可以相信」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是看見面麻的話 請溫柔對待她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很明白 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳 你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果沒有發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 好無趣 本來想找到面麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 肉烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集 為什麼一個人在烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}哇 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為是面麻拜託我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在我面前出現的時候說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請不要再引起騷動」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 面麻這麼說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽得不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望之類的 任性引起騷動 會不會添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢 面麻她...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻讓大家都聚集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回憶起面麻的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會一直 一直很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即時面麻現在不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都希望大家能一直 一直做好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 面麻 這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是放棄比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也許
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家 來 吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 蒸麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是仁碳媽媽經常做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...是面麻做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈做蒸麵包？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 那個 雖然是十分新穎的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是被嚇到也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或說我不正常也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻這麼說過 「大家如果能在一起 最開心了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說過「若能永不忘記 最開心了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再這個樣子可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都忘不了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被她束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃興了 之後大家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:06:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃蒸麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著十分誘人的香味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川看到面麻 是什麼的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 穿著白色的連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡有是不是有個小的蝴蝶結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 雖然記不太清楚 應該是這個樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 為什麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到面麻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個神秘的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集看到的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣子的面麻呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果面麻是面馬裡奧的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是面麻路易吉了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25}註釋：馬裡奧 路易吉 超級馬裡奧遊戲裡的倆兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2P顏色的話更好玩是吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 完全不明白雪集這傢伙的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請不要再引起騷動」太傷人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙有多愛妄想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最心痛的還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便曲解面麻的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是喜歡面麻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁...碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這裡有一個叫仁碳的好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好孩子頭頭的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是面麻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布偶和布偶人的妖精哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是一點也沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說仁碳啊 你喜歡面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 差不多該睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼看待我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸前有著蝴蝶結的連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話 白色 蝴蝶結的連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子 我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 仁太 今天收款的叔叔會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把抽屜第一層的錢給他就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個人的頭好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 那之後我都沒有去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}這人什麼也沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}要掉下去了 要掉下去了 危險 好危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人？  來收錢的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去學校了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 現在是去做文化家的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班是清歌合唱的咖啡店 你不認為很無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒變呢 真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼宿海君家是被爐還用地板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25}註釋：被爐，架上蓋上被，用以取暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 拿點心 來客人後要給客人點心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 只有巧克力茶點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蒸麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起宿海君母親做的能稍微硬點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是細麵粉篩選不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果試著用酵母我想應該會更鬆軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 原來面麻做的不好吃的原因不是葡萄乾放少了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會做料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理什麼的 只要掌握烹飪方法誰都會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻沒做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要份量和時機沒搞錯就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不弄到奇怪的地方...是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何而來啊 我只有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你說 這是面麻做的蒸麵包 果然不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也是啊 不相信是必然的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 就因如此 有件事想拜託仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你知道那傢伙說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你的腋下應該更好聞」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太老套了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 幹嘛 鳴子 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 突然想起有事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 關於鳴子 最近感覺和她相處變難了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 總感覺有點微妙得讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是宿海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道了吧 那個毛刺頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超和平剋星活動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要剋死掉虛偽的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳 真的要做嗎 為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期已經開始了 你還要這樣悠閒下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻吵著我出門晃晃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雪集 你看到的面麻是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的面麻啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不是 是在我家的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說你看到的面麻是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大家打算去秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..也帶面麻一起 可以的話你也一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你和以前的那個孩子王不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就算那時 我也沒認同你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨隨便便的就跟我搭話 敗家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 宿海君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給那傢伙看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明沒必要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也閒著 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要用這個嗎 在那一帶很癢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的 肌膚少露出一點就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳不是敗家犬 是很好的贏家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集看到的面麻也許不是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使出現另一個面麻也不奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為面麻為什麼會在這裡 也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？大家怎麼都聚在這？派對夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 快點把車燈關掉 太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不好意思 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好喝了 果然還是和灌裝咖啡不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母在義賣會買的新的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 雖然有點舊 但可以的話就在這用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把咖啡杯拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是大家聚在一起有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻這樣就感覺很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個也讓面麻喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在嗎 在這裡 在這裡 請喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉之後我考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻不是說 大家只要在一起就很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺這才是面麻說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深能領會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是「不想忘」...但怎麼能忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她就是易操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡波波了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣陣發冷 是咖啡喝多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小便大解放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}啊 面...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也去 一起小便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「忘記不了面麻」「一直被面麻束縛 你可真可憐」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鶴見子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集說的那些都是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鏈全開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 有了 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是面麻 是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡 這裡 快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊 確認過了的而且 看啊 鶴見子說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連衣裙啊 這裡帶有蝴蝶結的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繫蝴蝶結的連衣裙...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她 是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 一個人去太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休 休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到剛才為止 應該是在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 我們先回去趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那麼高個 就算把小腿毛剃光 也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 健酱拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:40.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:47.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:56.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}押花のしおり挟んで　君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:01:03.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:08.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}海を見渡す坂を駆け上って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:13.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:21.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:28.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:35.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}まだ二人はすぐそこにいるのに
